  displayName: 
  lines:
  - "The Big Bite\r\nThe Big Bite.\r\nThe Big Bite.\r\n\r\nThe Big Bite,[1] later
    known as The Bite of '83, was a similar incident shown in Five Nights at Freddy's
    4 during a cutscene after completing Night 5.[2] The events in the game took
    place in 1983. The main protagonist of the minigame, a crying child who is being
    thrown a party at Fredbear's Family Diner, is harshly tormented by a group of
    older kids, including his own brother. Aware of the child's deep-seated fear
    of the Springlock Animatronics, they deliberately exploit it, lifting and carrying
    him while he cries and struggles, forcing him closer to the stage. His brother
    then shoved the child's head entirely into Fredbear's mouth. As the child screams
    in terror, Fredbear\u2019s jaw suddenly snaps shut, crushing and causing a fatal
    injury. The bullies immediately stop laughing as the scene fades out"
  nextNode: {fileID: 0}
